<footer class="bg-primary-dark text-white pt-16">
  <div class="container max-w-300 mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[2fr_1fr_1fr] gap-12 mb-12">
    <div class="flex flex-col">
      <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-1">
        <span class="font-accent text-white text-[2.5rem]">Flores</span>
        <span class="font-main font-extrabold text-[1.8rem] text-white">Eternas</span>
      </a>
      <p class="mt-4 opacity-90 max-w-75">Flores que no se marchitan, hechas con creatividad y amor directamente desde Cancún.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h4 class="font-main font-semibold text-xl text-white mb-6">Enlaces Rápidos</h4>
      <ul class="list-none p-0 flex flex-col gap-3">
        <li><a href="/" class="opacity-80 transition-all duration-300 hover:opacity-100 hover:pl-1.25">Inicio</a></li>
        <li><a href="/nosotros" class="opacity-80 transition-all duration-300 hover:opacity-100 hover:pl-1.25">Sobre Nosotros</a></li>
        <li><a href="/catalogo" class="opacity-80 transition-all duration-300 hover:opacity-100 hover:pl-1.25">Catálogo</a></li>
        <li><a href="/personalizacion" class="opacity-80 transition-all duration-300 hover:opacity-100 hover:pl-1.25">Personalización</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h4 class="font-main font-semibold text-xl text-white mb-6">Síguenos</h4>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <a href="#" aria-label="Facebook" class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 bg-white/10 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-white hover:text-primary-dark hover:-translate-y-0.75">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3z"></path></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="#" aria-label="Instagram" class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 bg-white/10 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-white hover:text-primary-dark hover:-translate-y-0.75">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5" ry="5"></rect><path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"></path><line x1="17.5" y1="6.5" x2="17.51" y2="6.5"></line></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="bg-black/5 text-center p-6 text-sm opacity-80">
    <p>&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Flores Eternas Cancún. Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
